                    "text_PmB8Xp": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>Format</strong>: Adjustable knee brace with SLS™ tension dial: Left or right<br/><br/><strong>Weight</strong>: Approximately 280 g (ultra-light, invisible under clothing)<br/><br/><strong>Type</strong>: Advanced compression knee brace with patellar and lateral stabilization<br/><br/><strong>Benefits:</strong> <br/>✅ Relieves knee pain from the very first use<br/>✅ Stabilizes the patella and reduces joint pressure<br/>✅ Supports without restricting: regain your natural mobility<br/>✅ Prevents worsening of pain related to wear, sports or excess weight<br/><br/><strong>Unique features</strong>: <br/>✅ Integrated patellar GEL pad: absorbs impacts and protects the kneecap (not just basic compression)<br/>✅ Dual flexible steel lateral stabilizers: targeted support, no unwanted movement<br/>✅ SLS™ tension dial: adjust compression in 2 seconds without removing the brace<br/>✅ Anti-slip silicone grip: stays in place even after 12 hours of intense activity<br/><br/><strong>Contents</strong>: 1 Stabilix Pro™ knee brace (left or right)<br/><br/><strong>Easy to use</strong>: <br/>✅ Ready to wear: put it on, adjust it and move<br/>✅ Adjustable sizing: choose your size (M / L / XL / XXL) then fine-tune with the SLS™ dial<br/>✅ Breathable and thermoregulating fabric: designed for all-day extended wear</p>",
