                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>Shipping:</strong> <br/>Your packages are shipped within 1 to 2 business days, and home delivery takes 5 to 9 business days, depending on the shipping method chosen. Our team personally oversees the preparation and shipping of your orders, working with our logistics partners to ensure fast and secure delivery.<br/><br/><strong>Returns</strong>: <br/>We want every order to bring you complete satisfaction. If not, you have 30 days to return the product, for any reason. Our customer service team is available to help you and make the return process simple and quick.<br/><br/><strong>Additional information: </strong><br/>During periods of high demand, delivery times may be slightly longer, but don't worry! Our team will keep you informed by email so you know exactly when to expect your package.<br/><br/>For any questions, our team is available by email at info@sanoviaus.com. <br/>We're here to help!</p>",
