                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee or Your Money Back</strong><br/>At Sanovia, we believe in the quality of our products and in the complete satisfaction of our customers. That's why we offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee or your money back. <br/><br/><strong>How does it work?</strong> <br/>If for any reason you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, you have 30 days from receipt of your order to return it to us, and we will issue a full refund, no questions asked. You can shop with complete confidence, knowing there is zero risk.<br/><br/>This guarantee allows you to try our products at home, in your daily life, and see the quality for yourself. If this product doesn't meet your expectations, we simplify the return process to provide you with a smooth and pleasant customer experience.<br/><br/><strong>Our goal: your satisfaction. </strong><br/>Don't hesitate, place your order now and discover the Sanovia difference with the peace of mind that comes with our satisfaction guarantee.</p>",
