            },
            "text_P9FBba": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Its <strong>patellar GEL pad</strong> stabilizes the kneecap and absorbs every impact. </p><p><strong>Its dual flexible steel stabilizers</strong> prevent the lateral movements that worsen your pain. </p><p>Result: the joint stays <strong>in its natural axis, pressure is reduced immediately, and recovery is accelerated</strong>, whether after an injury, surgery or simply years of wear and tear.</p>",
