              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Zero slipping even after 12 hours. The silicone grip locks the brace in place. Zero discomfort. The thermoregulating fabric is worn under jeans, work pants or athletic shorts without anyone noticing. Zero hassle. The SLS™ dial adjusts compression in 2 seconds, without removing the brace. You don't feel it anymore. Neither does your knee.</p>",
